                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "$z_A-1=2\\left(\\cos\\frac{5\\pi}{6}+i\\sin\\frac{5\\pi}{6}\\right)$\n$z_C-1=2\\left(\\cos\\left(-\\frac{5\\pi}{6}\\right)+i\\sin\\left(-\\frac{5\\pi}{6}\\right)\\right)$\n$z_B=(2\\sqrt{3}-1)(\\cos\\pi+i\\sin\\pi)$"
