                  "text": "$\\lim_{n\\to+\\infty}u_n=\\lim_{n\\to+\\infty}\\left(\\frac{5}{1+\\frac{1}{4}\\left(-\\frac{2}{3}\\right)^n}-4\\right)=1$"
